<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>폼 전송 결과(실습)</title>
    <style>
      span {
        /* color: coral; */
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      li {
        border: 1px solid #bbb;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px #c8c8c8c8;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= title%>요청 확인하기</h1>
    <div><span><%=uersInfo.name%></span>님 환영합니다!</div>

    <ul>
      <li>성별: <%=uersInfo.gender%></li>
      <li>
        생년월일: <%=uersInfo.year%>/<%=uersInfo.month%>/<%=uersInfo.date%>
      </li>
      <li>관심사: <%=uersInfo.favorite%></li>
    </ul>

    <%if (addInfo){%>
    <h4>다른 태그 작성해보기</h4>
    <p>좋아하는 색깔:<span class="color"><%=uersInfo.color%></span></p>

    <p>좋아하는 숫자:<%=uersInfo.number%></p>
    <p>다짐 한마디:<%=uersInfo.comment%></p>
    <%}%>

    <script>
      // 이것도 안됨
      // p{
      //   color:<%=uersInfo.color%>
      // }

      document.addEventListener("DOMContntedLoaded", () => {
        const color = document.querySelector(".color");
        color.style.color = "<%=uersInfo.color%>";
      });
    </script>
